      "abstract": "Requires conditions placed on appropriations to the Stadium Development Special Fund to be met before expenditure.  Subjects expenditure by the Stadium Authority of an appropriation out of the Stadium Development Special Fund on the completion of specific project readiness conditions.  Appropriates moneys."
